doctype html
html
  head
    meta(name='viewport', content='initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no')
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    title Welcome
    // Our created js and css files
    script(src='//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.10.2.js')
    script(src='/javascripts/home.js')
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='/stylesheets/search.css')
    // Compiled and minified CSS
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.97.0/css/materialize.min.css')
    // Compiled and minified JavaScript
    script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.97.0/js/materialize.min.js')
    style.
      .parallax-container {
      height: "90px";
      }
    script.
      $(document).ready(function(){
      $('.parallax').parallax();
      });
  body
    // CREATING NAV BAR
    nav
      .nav-wrapper.cyan
        a.brand-logo(href='#', style='padding-left:60px;') MapYourTour
        ul#nav-mobile.right.hide-on-med-and-down
          // Modal Trigger
          li
            a.modal-trigger(href='#modal1') Log In
          // Modal Structure
          #modal1.modal.black-text
            .modal-content.center
              h4 Log In
              p Welcome back. Enter your username and password below.
            .modal-footer.center
              .row
                form.col.s12
                  .row
                    .input-field.col.s6
                      input#userName.validate(placeholder='Username', type='text')
                    .row
                      .input-field.col.s6
                        input#password.validate(placeholder='Password', type='password')
              a.modal-action.modal-close.waves-effect.waves-green.btn-flat(href='#!') Log In
    .parallax-container
      .parallax
        img(src='images/campus2.jpg')
      // MISSION STATEMENT
      p.center.flow-text.white-text(style='text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #000;')
        b Simplifying the process of planning a college trip.
    // SIGN UP
    br
    .center
      a.waves-effect.waves-light.btn(href='signup.html') Sign Up
    .container
      .section
        // Icon Section
        .row
          .col.s12.m4
            .icon-block
              // FIRST THIRD OF THE PAGE, THE PROBLEM
              h5.center The Problem
              p.light
                | We did most of the heavy lifting for you to provide a default stylings that incorporate our custom components. Additionally, we refined animations and transitions to provide a smoother experience for developers.
          // SECOND THIRD, THE SOLUTION
          .col.s12.m4
            .icon-block
              h5.center Our Solution
              p.light
                | We are planning to improve the process of scheduling and
                | booking college tours by putting all the necessary information in one
                | place: our website.  Our site will collect all the user’s information
                | when she or he signs up that would be needed for booking a college tour.
                | This way students don’t have to re-enter their information every time
                | they sign up for a tour, like they would normally do when booking on
                | individual colleges’ websites. Our website will also allow users to
                | search for colleges based on location, making it easier to book
                | multiple college tours, or allow the users to search by college name.
                | When the user searches the map, markers representing different colleges
                | will pop up onto the screen. When the user clicks on a marker, a brief
                | description of the college shows up on the side of the map, along with
                | basic statistics and a calendar with available tours and times. This
                | feature will give users the ability to schedule college tours with
                | colleges that they hadn’t planned on visiting prior to visiting our
                | website.
          // ABOUT US
          .col.s12.m4
            .icon-block
              h5.center About Us
              p.light
                b Hannah Lerner, MASSACHUSETTS
              p.light
                b Maddie Comtois, TEXAS
              p.light
                b Maddie Dick, CONNECTICUT
              p.light
                b Nora Mitchell, NEW YORK
  // FOOTER
  footer.page-footer.cyan
    .container.white-text
      .row
        .col.l6.s12
          // CONTACT US
          h5.white-text Contact Us
          ul
            li
              | Email: 
              a.grey-text.text-lighten-3(href='#!') MapYourTour@gmail.com
            li
              | Instagram: 
              a.grey-text.text-lighten-3(href='https://instagram.com/mapyourtour/') @MapYourTour
            li
              | Facebook: 
              a.grey-text.text-lighten-3(href='#!') Map Your Tour
            li
              | Twitter: 
              a.grey-text.text-lighten-3(href='https://twitter.com/MapYourTour') @MapYourTour
    .footer-copyright
      .container
        | © 2015 Copyright MapYourTour
        a.grey-text.text-lighten-4.right(href='#!') Home
